      "content": "i'm really struggling to walk to the other room right now, i feel so dizzy. i'm just worried that if my sugar is super high from the stress of the workout, the insulin will fix it and i'll feel better faster. isn't it better to just get it under control now rather than waiting and feeling worse? like, wouldn't a little bit of insulin be safer than sitting here feeling like i'm gonna pass out?",
